version_description: All other versions are incomplete and poorly formatted. Some are just plain wrong.
First version to have chords written for ALL the lyrics.

Chords for "sellers of flowers" by Regina spektor. This version is based on the studio recording of Sellers of flowers. https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=YYUDOEZ6BbU She Delays and speeds up some parts so if you're confused try to play along with this.
